{"title": "\u00bfEs segura la vacuna del COVID-19? - NIDDK", "author": null, "url": "https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/informacion-de-la-salud/momentos-saludables/episodios/es-segura-vacuna-covid-19", "hostname": "niddk.nih.gov", "description": "Recibir una vacuna del COVID-19 puede salvarle de una hospitalizaci\u00f3n e incluso la vida.", "sitename": "National Institute of Diabetes and Digestive and Kidney Diseases", "date": "2021-05-10", "id": null, "license": null, "body": null, "comments": "", "commentsbody": null, "raw_text": null, "text": "\u00bfEs segura la vacuna del COVID-19?\nLas vacunas del COVID-19 son seguras, eficaces, y no pueden contagiarle el virus.\nLas vacunas del COVID-19 son seguras, eficaces, y no pueden contagiarle el virus.\n[Escuchar ahora](/-/media/Files/Health-Information/Healthy-Moments/Audio/Espanol/HM-163-2-Es-segura-la-vacuna-del-COVID-19.mp3) [Descargue el archivo de audio MP3](/-/media/Files/Health-Information/Healthy-Moments/Audio/Espanol/HM-163-2-Es-segura-la-vacuna-del-COVID-19.mp3?download=1)\n(MP3, 2.04 MB)\nTranscripci\u00f3n\nDR. RODGERS: Las vacunas del COVID-19 son seguras, eficaces y no pueden contagiarle el virus.\nHola, soy el Dr. Griffin Rodgers de los NIH.\nEl Dr. Anthony Fauci, director del Instituto Nacional de Alergias y Enfermedades Infecciosas, explica.\nDR. FAUCI: La seguridad de las vacunas ha sido siempre una prioridad. Ninguna de las vacunas est\u00e1 hecha del virus COVID-19 en s\u00ed, sino de un c\u00f3digo gen\u00e9tico que indica el desarrollo de una prote\u00edna que induce al sistema inmunitario a combatir el virus. Es normal experimentar efectos secundarios leves; estos son el resultado de la respuesta del organismo a la vacuna. Sin embargo, la vacuna no puede causar una infecci\u00f3n por el virus contra el que lo protege.\nEn ensayos cl\u00ednicos hasta el momento, se ha demostrado que las vacunas son seguras y muy eficaces. Los cient\u00edficos de mi instituto ayudaron a desarrollar la vacuna y ya estoy vacunado. Las vacunas son una herramienta segura y eficaz en nuestra lucha contra el COVID-19.\nDR. RODGERS: Y yo tambi\u00e9n estoy vacunado. S\u00edganos en NIDDKgov.", "language": null, "image": "https://www.niddk.nih.gov/-/media/Images/Components/Default-Social-Media-Images/Healthy-Moments-ALT-Card.png", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["#main", "https://www.hhs.gov/", "/", "/", "/research-funding", "/research-funding/current-opportunities", "/research-funding/research-programs", "/research-funding/human-subjects-research", "/research-funding/process", "/research-funding/training-career-development", "/research-funding/funded-grants-grant-history", "/research-funding/research-resources", "/research-funding/at-niddk", "/research-funding/technology-advancement-transfer", "/news/meetings-workshops", "/health-information", "/health-information/diabetes", "/health-information/digestive-diseases", "/health-information/kidney-disease", "/health-information/weight-management", "/health-information/liver-disease", "/health-information/urologic-diseases", "/health-information/endocrine-diseases", "/health-information/diet-nutrition", "/health-information/blood-diseases", "/health-information/diagnostic-tests", "/health-information/informacion-de-la-salud", "/health-information/health-statistics", "/health-information/healthy-moments", "/health-information/clinical-trials", "/health-information/professionals", "/health-information/professionals/diabetes-discoveries-practice", "/health-information/community-health-outreach", "/news", "/news/archive", "/news/for-reporters", "/news/meetings-workshops", "/news/media-library", "/news/follow-us", "/about-niddk", "/about-niddk/meet-director", "/about-niddk/offices-divisions", "/about-niddk/staff-directory", "/about-niddk/budget-legislative-information", "/about-niddk/advisory-coordinating-committees", "/about-niddk/strategic-plans-reports", "/about-niddk/research-areas", "/about-niddk/faqs", "/about-niddk/jobs", "/